data.description: This Meticulously maintained and fully renovated home offers a beautiful blend of modern elegance and functionality. Step inside your state of the art custom dream kitchen boasting top of the line ss appliances, including a 6 burner wolf  gas oven, Omega Wood cabinetry, Lieber side by side refridg, beverage refridge and more! This kitchen  is where all will gather to enjoy! Radiant flooring in the kitchen,dining and lower level expanded den adds an extra touch and comfort of luxury in the home. 9 Holly offers all newer bathrooms.Full finished lower level w storage and extra living space.  The front entrance has has been renovated this year and offers new pavers, plantings and lighting to create a lovely curb  appeal.(No garage) 2022 renovation includes backyard fence, brand new 8x10 shed  and new small trex deck  creating privacy and  wonderful outdoor space on this large flat  parcel (77x135) with room for a large pool if you choose. Located in the town of Syosset, this home is  near by food shopping, Dining,  major transportation, Syosset Library, Town Community pool and more! Schedule a showing with me today to view this lovely new opportunity to live in Syosset Groves.
